ReferenceDocuments.name: Specify the other growth fact
ReferenceDocuments.description: Specify the other growth factor treatment that the donor received to enhance the product collection:

ReferenceDocuments.name: BRIDG mapping path for CDE:2772167
ReferenceDocuments.description: "PerformedProcedure > DefinedProcedure.nameCode(CD).originalText [1, some pre-collection therapy] WHERE  PerformedProcedure > DefinedProcedure [1] > DefinedCompositionRelationship [2] > DefinedProcedure [3] > DefinedCompositionRelationship [4] > DefinedProcedure [5] AND DefinedProcedure.nameCode(CD).nullFlavor = ""OTH"" AND DefinedProcedure.reasonCode [1] = ""enhance product collection""  AND DefinedProcedure.nameCode [3] = ""harvest composite activity"" AND DefinedProcedure.nameCode [5] = ""extract stem cell harvest"" AND DefinedCompositionRelationship.sequenceNumber [2] IS LESS THAN DefinedCompositionRelationship.sequenceNumber [4]"
